floppy disks, the software emulates the floppy drive as well. It uses files with a .adf 
suffix as replacement for floppy disks. Adf stands for Amiga Disk File. ADF Opus' reason 
for being is to allow these disk files to be manipulated directly from Windows.
\par
\par
UAE is available for a number of platforms including Mac, BeBox, NextStep, Amiga, pOS, 
XFree86/OS2, Acorn RISC PC, Win32 and DOS. Further details can be obtained from one of the 
UAE web sites. 
\par
\par
